               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 21. - <rs id="t18300415-290-punish1586" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300415-290-punish1586" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300415-290-defend2459 t18300415-290-punish1586"></join>
               Transported for Seven Years
            </rs>.</p>
